Setup and Running

    1.clone the repository
        git clone https://github.com/Nahid-ghorbani/graph-task-manager.git
        cd graph-task-manager

    2.Build and run with docker-compose.yml file
        docker compose up --build

    3.Accessing to app on localhost
        app: http://localhost:8080
        postgres: http://localhost:5444 >> psql -h localhost -p 5444 -U graph -d gtm-db

    ** For running app on local you can use Follow command on root path:
        go run ./cmd/task-manager

    ** The app waits for the database to be ready before starting, wait until see the success message.

Testing

    For testing app after running it on local machine, just run follow command:
    make test
